{"tid":1603264,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"建議整個「我們都是臥底」hashtag campaign","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T17:39:05.000Z","uid":207710,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0b9593cdfc9377cfac320b6556923589b53f09","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"今日肯定有捉錯鬼搞到內鬥嘅情況<br />\n講真大家都知有臥底<br />\n但亂咁捉鬼仲衰過畀臥底捉<br />\n呢個風氣蔓延落去非常危險<br />\n民記都有手足講過點都唔好捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n我覺得無去過違法集會嘅和理非可以整個類似 #Eye4HK嘅campaign<br />\n去推動一啲跟得唔貼嘅手足明白唔捉鬼嘅重要性<br />\n唔好信一啲瘋傳嘅fake news去捉鬼<br />\n就算有鬼，等事後先講<br />\n呢類hashtag campaign前線唔好參加<br />\n以免disclose身份<br />\n希望咁樣嘅campaign可以導正呢個歪風<br />\n令呢場時代革命走得更長更遠<br />\n<br />\n認同嘅幫推，唔該"},{"pid":"5aa5426235ab078e2c4ca70a242d81dc733ef951","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"當然用咩用字或者hastag可以再諗諗"},{"pid":"c1c01810665e4b3924fea6851cbddc108fdea799","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"我只係brainstorm個idea"},{"pid":"feb5dc9405af1ecce2a39df771b857f30a734eee","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"大家唔同意<br />\n或者覺得應該繼續捉鬼<br />\n都可以討論吓"},{"pid":"32a1ac7962e35578ba46d0003c16b7af0e995de9","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8802ffe6cabd58b71fff25736657b6920791c14a","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:49:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95da0801d962748117c68c50b0da4fad11e78e3e","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42777bf0552b19b7eeed696749a9b7e09c1e0921","tid":1603264,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:50:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid"